parameters.text:
=Generate the full AI image prompt for a GilgitApp marketing Tweet Card using the data below.

Use the exact Twitter/X card mockup style as described in the system instructions.

Input data:

Text on image: {{ $('Switch').item.json['Text on Image'] }}

SEO keywords / Hashtags: {{ $('Switch').item.json['SEO Keywords '] }}

Important rules:

Use the uploaded logo for GilgitApp (do NOT describe the logo)

Include the tweet text and hashtags clearly

Output only valid JSON

Output format:

{
  "ai_image_prompt": "..."
}

