parameters.text:
=Generate a Facebook post text for GilgitApp using the following input JSON:

Post title: {{ $json['Blog Title '] }}
Main idea: {{ $json['Main Idea / Topic'] }}
SEO keywords: {{ $json['SEO Keywords '] }}

About GilgitApp:
GilgitApp is a free online marketplace where users can buy and sell cars, bikes, mobiles, laptops, property, and more.

Output Format (JSON only):

{
  "facebook_post": "..."
}

parameters.jsonBody:
={
  "query": "mutation CreateDraft { createPost(input: { text: \"{{ $('AI Agent3').item.json.output.facebook_post }}\", channelId: \"62000dafc2bd2585f9011a72\", schedulingType: automatic, mode: addToQueue, saveToDraft: true, metadata: { facebook: { type: post } }, assets: { images: [{ url: \"{{ $json.url }}\" }] } }) { ... on PostActionSuccess { post { id text status assets { ... on ImageAsset { source thumbnail } } } } ... on InvalidInputError { message } ... on UnauthorizedError { message } ... on UnexpectedError { message } } }"
}

={
